(79, 'Business 2 Community', 'http://www.business2community.com/', 'B2B.jpg', 2011, 290, 2, 3, 1, 2600000, 6, 6492, 0, '2015-11-10 03:05:57', 'com', 83.36, '2015-11-10 03:05:24', '<p>Business 2 Community (B2C)&nbsp; is one of the most popular business communities and info websites about business in Internet. Since 2012 the site became a leader among business websites on the web according to Technorati and Alexa.com. It''s notable that B2C is a Google News Site and many authoritative sites, including Yahoo! Small Business, make re-posts of a content of this website.<strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Important:</strong><br />Only for tech websites.<br /><strong></strong></p>'),
(80, '10 Steps', 'http://10steps.sg/', '10Steps.jpg', 2008, 250, 1, 1, 1, 190000, 5, 118314, 0, '2015-05-26 22:30:22', 'sg', 54.75, '2015-05-26 22:19:45', '<p>10Steps.SG - website for web designers and for everyone interested in new waves in web design. Site exists from 2008 and all published posts move through the main page. It''s a great resource for posts publications in web design niche.</p>'),
(81, 'Smashing Hub', 'http://smashinghub.com/', 'SmashingHub.jpg', 2010, 750, 1, 1, 2, 320000, 5, 63009, 0, '2015-10-18 17:38:30', 'com', 57.52, '2015-10-18 17:38:32', '<p>Smashing Hub - famous web blog and website for web designers, graphic designers, photographers and other artist. Website contains premium tips, tutorials, tools, web apps and resources. 75% of traffic website gets from search engines. It''s a great resource for posts publications in web design, web development, photography, inspirations niches.</p>'),
(82, 'About.com', 'http://www.about.com/', 'about.jpg', 1999, 650, 1, 1, 0, 182500000, 7, 188, 1, '2015-12-02 23:12:43', 'com', 90.02, '2015-12-02 23:12:44', '<p>About.com - is one of the most authoritative and highly visited info websites in the world. Site covers all possible topic that might be interesting to a reader - from cockroach races to artificial intelligence. Over 1000 experts fill About.com and each of them is an accredited and qualified professional in their field. About.com exists since 1999 and its materials are willingly reposted by all sorts of websites, including translations on other languages.</p>'),
(83, 'Forbes', 'http://www.forbes.com/', 'Forbes.jpg', 1993, 2900, 1, 3, 2, 66200000, 8, 166, 0, '2015-11-24 20:31:59', 'com', 95.3, '2015-11-24 20:32:00', '<p>Forbes.com - is a website of one of the most respected and well-known economic&nbsp; publications of the world founded in 1917. Website Forbes.com exists since 1993 and for this time became a leader among financial and business news websites. Materials of the website are frequently reposted by many other business publications and info sites. Having traffic over 70 millions per months, half this traffic Forbes.com receives from search engines.</p>'),
(84, 'The Huffington Post', 'http://www.huffingtonpost.com/', 'huffingtonpost.jpg', 2005, 2500, 1, 1, 1, 163500000, 8, 122, 0, '2015-12-16 15:02:11', 'com', 95.88, '2015-12-16 15:00:58', '<p>Huffingtonpost.com- is one of the most popular news websites these days, and presents the most current topics in an easy-to-read and engaging style. Its top quality content is frequently reposted by sites like Yahoo! Huffingtonpost.com is one of the most frequently visited news sites on the web, with separate editions in different countries. Its amazing quality of content is proven by its high traffic, which exceeds 240 million per month. It has been bringing its readers all the latest news from fields like international headlines, sports, and entertainment, among others, since 2005. Most of its traffic is received through search engines, social media and other referring sites, like Wikipedia.</p>'),
(85, 'Mashable', 'http://mashable.com/', 'Mashable.jpg', 2005, 1600, 1, 3, 2, 48400000, 8, 297, 0, '2015-11-14 16:04:37', 'com', 96.42, '2015-11-10 03:10:06', '<p>Mashable.com - is a popular website which brings to its readers all the latest news regarding trending topics, right from Game of Thrones to new apps, and others. It is one of the most frequently visited sites, especially in the U.S. It attracts traffic of over 48 million every month. It has been keeping people in touch with the recent happenings and events, ever since its creation, way back in the year 2005. Its content is readily reposted by sites like Time, Harper&rsquo;s Bazaar and Lifehacker. It receives its traffic via search engines and more so, from social media platforms like Facebook and Reddit.&nbsp;</p>'),
(86, 'The Epoch Times', 'http://www.theepochtimes.com/', 'epochtimes.jpg', 2003, 290, 1, 1, 0, 1800000, 6, 27482, 0, '2015-11-10 02:58:48', 'com', 82.11, '2015-11-10 02:58:49', '<p>Theepochtimes.com - is an online news forum, which is available in 35 countries across the globe as well as in 21 different languages. It undertakes a discussion based approach to news headlines through its online forums. The website came into being way back in the year 2003, and has gone on to achieve great popularity among news-readers, with monthly traffic exceeding 1.8 million. Its content is regularly re-posted by sites like Rense, Fark and Wikipedia, among others. It receives the bulk of its traffic via search engines, especially Google, and social networks, such as Facebook and Reddit, to name a few.</p>'),
(87, 'Lucky Сommunity', 'http://community.luckyshops.com/', 'lucky.jpg', 2002, 200, 1, 1, 1, 35000, 0, 13311, 0, '2015-05-27 01:10:21', 'com', 44.66, '2015-05-27 01:10:22', '<p>Lucky Сommunity - is an online fashion and style community, which gives an in-depth look into the fresh fashion scenes and the hottest trends in the fashion circle. Viewers can become members and contribute to the website&rsquo;s content. Its traffic estimates are slated at around 4,000 every month. Its popularity has been increasing steadily among fashion lovers, ever since it was created in 2000. Its content is frequently shared by sites like Huaren and Cisionpoint. Many individual bloggers also refer to this site for valuable content and information regarding fashion trends. Search engines and social sites like Facebook and Pinterest are a major source of its traffic.</p>'),
(88, 'Examiner.com', 'http://www.examiner.com/', 'examiner.jpg', 1994, 190, 2, 1, 1, 13100000, 8, 1645, 0, '2015-05-27 01:18:18', 'com', 90.61, '2015-05-27 01:18:20', '<p>Examiner.com - is a one-stop entertainment and lifestyle website, which was created all the way back in the year 1994. It has separate sections, such as videos, leisure, auto, and the likes, for visitors to explore the site, according to their own interests. It attracts traffic exceeding 33 million, each month. The websites that frequently re-post its contents include the likes of IMDB, N4g and Newsnow, to name a few. It attracts its traffic mostly through search engines. Facebook is also a major source of its traffic. According to Similar Web, it ranks 501st in the news and media category of websites.</p>'),
(89, 'Lifehack', 'http://www.lifehack.org/', 'lifehack.jpg', 2005, 350, 1, 3, 1, 10600000, 6, 1786, 0, '2015-11-10 02:59:56', 'org', 82.72, '2015-11-10 02:59:56', '<p>Lifehack - is one of the most popular online assistance websites with tips and life hacks relevant to various aspects of an individual&rsquo;s day-to-day life. It has a host of credible authors who contribute articles on different fields in which one may require guidance or knowledge. It is one of the frequently visited help sites and has a monthly traffic that exceeds the 18 million mark. It was created in the year 2005 and is based in Virginia, United States. Its quality content is often re-posted by websites like Feedly, Imgur, among others. Its traffic is directed mostly through search engines, like Google, and social networking media.</p>'),
(90, 'Venturebeat', 'http://venturebeat.com/', 'vb.jpg', 2005, 350, 1, 1, 2, 10600000, 7, 2423, 2, '2016-03-24 12:37:09', 'com', 88.44, '2016-03-24 12:37:11', '<p>Venturebeat - is a popular website that deals with all sorts of news and trends regarding technology. Its tagline says, &ldquo;Tech News that Matter&rdquo;, and it brings to its viewers just that. With traffic of over 11 million every month, it is one of the most frequently visited websites in the technology category. It was created in the year 2005 and continues to enjoy large scale popularity due to its quality content. Its content has often been re-posted by popular sites like Feedly, Techmeme and Wikipedia. The bulk of its traffic is received through search engines, mainly through Google.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important:</strong><br />Only for game websites.</p>'),
(91, 'Social Media Today ', 'http://www.socialmediatoday.com/', 'SocialMediaToday.jpg', 2006, 350, 2, 3, 2, 1900000, 6, 8349, 0, '2015-10-18 17:29:17', 'com', 86.94, '2015-10-18 17:29:19', '<p>Social Media Today - is a website that deals with one of the most talked-about subjects today: social media. It provides everything that one wants to know about social media- new sites, marketing strategies as well as webinars. Its increasing popularity across the cyber-space is evidenced by the 1 million visitors it receives on an approximate, each month. Most of these visitors are directed to the site through search engines, such as the likes of Google, social networking sites and display advertisements. Its contents are frequently reposted by sites like Feedly, Quicksprout and Creationagency, to name a few. It was created way back in 2006.</p>'),
(92, 'Inspirationfeed', 'http://inspirationfeed.com/', 'inspirationfeed.jpg', 2010, 350, 1, 1, 1, 490000, 2, 32866, 0, '2015-05-27 01:49:13', 'com', 59.04, '2015-05-27 01:49:14', '<p>Inspirationfeed - is an online creative market, which deals with all sorts of information and topics on the creative front, from different font styles to B-n-B rentals. It is a good place to start for individuals who are looking to re-modify and beautify their websites. It has a monthly traffic of about 500 thousand. The content featured on this website has often been reposted by sites such as the likes of Getprismatic, Feedly and Designspiration, among various others. Its traffic originates mostly via search engines, namely Google.</p>'),
(93, 'Instructables', 'http://www.instructables.com/', 'instructables.jpg', 2005, 150, 2, 1, 1, 34300000, 6, 524, 0, '2015-11-04 23:54:32', 'com', 91.04, '2015-11-04 23:54:32', '<p>Instructables - is an online instructional community that helps interested individuals by providing them with step-by-step instructions that helps them create a variety of interesting and unique things, ranging from discreet hiding places to remote controlled toys. It was created in the year 2006 and has won praises for its easy guidance procedures. Its popularity is well evidenced by its high traffic that exceeds the 50 million mark on a monthly basis. Well known sites like Lifehacker and Buzzfeed are some of the few that often re-post information from this site. It depends mainly on search engines for the majority of traffic it receives.</p>'),
(94, 'B2B Marketing', 'http://www.b2bmarketing.net/', 'B2B Marketing.jpg', 2003, 250, 1, 3, 1, 230000, 4, 43762, 0, '2015-05-28 00:25:30', 'net', 60.76, '2015-05-28 00:25:31', '<p>B2B Marketing - is an online forum, dealing with the business and corporate marketing and advertising sphere. It contains a detailed report on the current case studies, important business &ldquo;how-to&rsquo;s&rdquo; and discussions. They even host business summits and training seminars in different parts of the world. It was created in the year 2003 and has since, grown to become one of the most frequently visited business marketing websites, with over 200 thousand visitors every month. Its content is often re-posted by sites like Feedly and Newsnow. Search engines, such as the likes of Google, are its major source of traffic.</p>'),
(95, 'Wamda', 'http://wamda.com/', 'wamda.jpg', 2005, 48, 1, 1, 2, 290000, 5, 17344, 0, '2015-12-08 01:34:49', 'com', 57.88, '2015-12-08 01:34:51', '<p>Wamda - is an online help and news forum for entrepreneurs and businessmen. Since the site was opened to public access in 2005, it has emerged as one of the leading business websites across the cyber-sphere. It attracts a monthly traffic of nearly 300 thousand. It has an exceptionally large following in India. It helps keep businessmen in the loop regarding latest corporate happenings and also assists them in any entrepreneurial issue that they might have. Sites like Feedly and Sasapost often refer to information published on Wamda. Its traffic mainly originates through search engines such as Google, and social media, namely Facebook and Twitter.</p>'),
(96, 'Glipho', 'http://glipho.com/', 'glipho.jpg', 2012, 90, 1, 1, 0, 130000, 4, 71801, 0, '2015-11-01 18:32:26', 'com', 57.06, '2015-11-01 18:32:27', '<p>Glipho - is a social blogging website, designed to help aspiring writers work on their blogging skills and expand their readership at the same time. It is a blogging platform that allows its users to write and post their stories online to share with the world. Its popularity is on a sharp upward slope, with traffic of nearly 130 thousand, on a monthly basis. It is often referred to by websites like Blackhatworld. The majority of its high traffic originates through search engines, like Google, and to a certain extent, through social media, namely Pinterest.</p>'),
(97, 'Bubblews', 'http://www.bubblews.com/', 'bubblews.jpg', 2011, 48, 1, 1, 1, 910000, 4, 15218, 1, '2015-10-18 17:27:12', 'com', 66.95, '2015-10-18 17:27:14', '<p>Bubblews - is a social blogging platform that allows its users to post their thoughts and share them with the world. Users also have the added benefit of commenting and sharing another user&rsquo;s article. It has a monthly traffic that is near about the 1 million mark. This proves its immense popularity among aspiring bloggers. Its content is very frequently shared by sites like Lifehacker and Beforeitsnew, among various others. It is mainly dependant on search engines such as the likes of Google for its high flow of traffic.</p>'),
(98, 'YourTango', 'http://www.yourtango.com/', 'YourTango.jpg', 2007, 250, 2, 3, 1, 5000000, 6, 6350, 0, '2015-05-28 16:08:24', 'com', 72.21, '2015-05-28 16:00:10', '<p>Yourtango - is an online community for women, which imparts various helpful advices and tips on love and relationships to different categories of women- single, dating, married or breaking up. It is a forum for women to seek help regarding their love lives. It was created in the year 2007 and in only 8 years of being in service, it attracts an estimated number of around 5 million visitors on a monthly basis. Frequently visited sites like the Huffingtonpost and Psychcentral, among others, have often re-posted content featured on the pages of this website. Its main sources of traffic are search engines, especially Google, and social media sites, namely Facebook.</p>'),
(99, 'Sofeminine', 'http://www.sofeminine.co.uk/', 'sofeminine.jpg', 2004, 150, 1, 3, 1, 920000, 5, 26531, 0, '2015-05-28 16:15:13', 'uk', 57.86, '2015-05-28 16:15:14', '<p>Sofeminine - is a female-centric website that deals with lifestyle, entertainment fashion and other areas that are relevant to the typical female&rsquo;s life. It was created way beck in the year 2004 and in the 11 years of its existence, it has garnered an extraordinarily large and strong fan base. It attracts traffic of around 92 thousand, every month. It deals with a variety of areas of female interest, ranging from styles to relationships, beauty to fitness, and a host of other fields. Its content is often reposted by sites like Velvet, Cosmo and Deadspin, among others. Its traffic is mainly directed through search engines.</p>'),
(100, 'Houzz', 'http://www.houzz.com/', 'houzz.jpg', 2006, 290, 1, 1, 1, 17000000, 6, 576, 0, '2015-06-13 17:32:52', 'com', 93.31, '2015-06-13 17:32:54', '<p>Houzz - is a website that provides home styling, redecorating and modeling ideas and inspirations. It features a ton of inspirational design schemes and themes for different types of houses, as suited to the visitor&rsquo;s own home. It was created in the year 2006. By virtue of its immensely high quality and vast scope of content, it attracts traffic of roughly around 20 million, on a monthly basis. Its content is frequently shared by sites like Feedly and Gardenweb, to name a few. Its traffic is mostly directed through search engines, namely Google.</p>'),
(101, 'BlogHer', 'http://www.blogher.com/', 'BlogHer.jpg', 2003, 250, 1, 3, 1, 530000, 6, 18942, 0, '2015-12-23 23:59:57', 'com', 82.45, '2015-12-23 23:59:57', '<p>BlogHer - is a social blogging platform, mainly centered on women. It deals with a variety of issues that women face on a daily basis, ranging from marriage problems to children issues. SimilarWeb has ranked it number 862 on the list of websites, falling in the category of People and Society. It attracts a rough number of around 840 thousand visitors on a monthly basis. It is especially popular in the United States. Its content is commonly shared by well-known sites like Forbes, Feedly and Buzzfeed, to name a few. It depends heavily on search engines and social networking sites for most of its traffic.</p>'),
(102, 'Ground Report', 'http://groundreport.com/', 'groundreport.jpg', 2006, 180, 1, 1, 1, 40000, 3, 114856, 0, '2015-05-28 21:16:51', 'com', 54.51, '2015-05-28 21:16:52', '<p>Ground Report - is an international news platform with a unique twist &ndash; almost anyone is able to publish videos and news reports in order to get a share of the ad revenues. Every contributor retains the right to their work and gain community feedback which enhances the appeal of the website among budding journalists and reporters. Close to 40k people visit the website and it currently ranks 685,352 around the world. The site was established as late as 2006 but continues to remain a haven for interesting news reports seen from the lens of the masses. The content of the site is regularly shared by other websites.</p>'),
(103, 'JustLuxe', 'http://www.justluxe.com/', 'justluxe.jpg', 2004, 150, 2, 3, 1, 320000, 5, 53685, 1, '2016-01-19 00:07:11', 'com', 53.96, '2016-01-19 00:07:12', '<p>JustLuxe - is a luxury publication on the Internet that aims to provide objective analysis and details to wealthy consumers of luxury travel, goods and services. The website offers access to the Affluent Lifestyle Guide which is a treasure trove of insight and content into different categories, including yacht, luxury travel and aircraft charter services, fashion trends and news, vacation and real estate. Launched in 2005, the site has remained one of the best online luxury guides and reviews and receives over 320,000 visitors. The high quality content of the site is reposted by various web portals, including HuffingtonPost, Pulse and CrunchBase.</p>'),
(104, 'BecomeGorgeous', 'http://www.becomegorgeous.com/', 'becomegorgeous.jpg', 2006, 90, 1, 1, 1, 250000, 5, 86114, 0, '2015-10-18 17:30:22', 'com', 54.03, '2015-10-18 17:30:25', '<p>BecomeGorgeous - provides you with access to online health and beauty tips for a smarter, healthier and more gorgeous you. Users of the site can enjoy instant access to numerous beauty tips, the latest makeup, hairstyles and fashion trends, and shopping tricks. The website caters to every aspect of the user&rsquo;s beauty routine, along with natural skin and hair care treatments to celebrity style pictures. This wholesome approach of the website has landed its content on popular sites like Mashable and PitchEngine. The site receives over 250,000 visitors and has continued to remain active since its launch in 2006, ranking 56,336 in the United States.</p>'),
