(136, 'Kinja', 'https://kinja.com/', 'kinja.jpg', 2002, 150, 1, 1, 1, 11700000, 0, 1797, 0, '2015-07-12 19:02:49', 'com', 75.31, '2015-07-12 19:02:50', '<p>Kinja - is a compilation of a variety of mini blogs and mobile apps, sponsored by Gawker Media. The website, founded in 2002, reels in a surprising 8.70 million visitors every month, with a bounce rate of above 55%. A majority of visitors are from the U.S, but the site caters to guests from over 170 countries and gets nearly 63% of its traffic from referrals and only 20% from direct site visits. The content on Kinja.com is regularly reposted on sites like Gimodo.com and Feedly.com.</p>'),
