(138, 'Inspirefirst', 'http://www.inspirefirst.com/', 'inspirefirst.jpg', 2010, 90, 1, 1, 1, 90000, 4, 125690, 0, '2015-10-18 18:48:34', 'com', 44.52, '2015-10-18 18:48:36', '<p>Inspirefirst - is one of the internet&rsquo;s premier inspirations sharing websites and gives users the ability to share their inspiration on a blog publishing-style website. The site attracts about 220,000 users every month since its creation in 2010. It caters to visitors from over 125 countries and attracts most if its traffic via search engine results. The site is fairly new and suffers from a bounce rate of about 75%. One can often find inspirefirst.com content being reposted on websites like Feedly.com and Abduzeedo.com.</p>'),
(139, 'WebDesignersBlog.net', 'http://www.webdesignersblog.net/', 'webdesignersblog.jpg', 2010, 90, 1, 1, 1, 25000, 3, 253091, 0, '2015-10-18 18:49:14', 'net', 37.65, '2015-10-18 18:49:15', '<p>WebDesignersBlog.net - is a world leading design blog that was created in 2010. The website focuses on all things design-based, right from inspiration, tutorials, trends, digital art works and vector downloads. The page attracts about 40,000 visitors a month, most of which are from the U.S. It also receives guests from over 110 countries and most of its traffic, over 85%, comes from search engine results and only about 3% coming from referrals to the site. The content from this site is regularly reposted on websites like W3cplus.com and Brunovila.com.</p>');
