(140, 'Purevolume', 'http://www.purevolume.com/', 'PureVolume.jpg', 2003, 90, 1, 1, 1, 330000, 3, 12836, 0, '2015-10-18 18:50:04', 'com', 86.22, '2015-10-18 18:50:05', '<p>Purevolume &ndash; originally known as Unborn Media, PureVolume was the first independent website which allowed the streaming and uploading of audio files. It was launched in 2003 and acquired by SpinMedia in 2010. It is an ideal website for the discovery and promotion of new music, and an excellent tool for emerging artists, specifically those focusing on non-mainstream or indie genres of music. PureVolume, responsible for the discovery of a number of new bands, has been referred to as a &lsquo;new chapter in the world of music&rsquo;, and is attributed with the rise of a number of indie bands. With an estimated number of 360000 visits and referrals from sites such as Refhide and Absolutepunk, this website is one to watch.</p>'),
(141, 'EmpowHER', 'http://www.empowher.com/', 'EmpowHER.jpg', 2007, 150, 2, 1, 1, 1800000, 6, 34794, 0, '2015-07-13 14:17:53', 'com', 50.48, '2015-07-13 14:17:56', '<p>EmpowHER, founded in 2007 by Michelle King Robson, is a company and website dedicated to the health and well-being of women everywhere. A private organization, it provides women with the medical resources that they need, such as health information, supportive advocates, and a nurturing community. EmpowHER is most popular with American women, with 77.74% of their 4.2 million visitors from the United States. 55.93% of their traffic is from searches, and 100% of searches are organic. As a health resource for women, EmpowHER has a great deal to offer, and the team has received a number of awards and other recognition for their work. 55.93% of their traffic is from search engines, with reposts on Facebook, Reddit and Twitter.</p>'),
(142, 'RebelMouse', 'https://www.rebelmouse.com/', 'rebelmouse.jpg', 2004, 48, 1, 1, 1, 700000, 6, 15079, 1, '2016-03-15 15:19:39', 'com', 83.01, '2015-10-18 18:50:49', '<p>RebelMouse allows users to convert their social streams into personalized and dynamic homepages. Subscribers can connect it to their Twitter and Facebook accounts for an integrated social media strategy. Current traffic is up to 930000, with 39.41% direct traffic, 22.80% from referrals and another 20.28% from search engines. Reposts are available from websites such as Techcrunch, Socialmediaexaminer and several others. RebelMouse is the brainchild of Paul Berry, famous in tech circles as the reason for The Huffington Post&rsquo;s smashing success in search engine optimization as well as social media. RM is expected to help users replicate that success, but on an individual level.</p>'),
(143, 'CalorieCount ', 'http://www.caloriecount.com/', 'caloriecount.jpg', 2002, 250, 1, 1, 1, 3200000, 6, 5780, 0, '2015-07-15 13:00:03', 'com', 44.88, '2015-07-15 13:00:04', '<p>Founded in 2002, CalorieCount maintains a database of more than 250,000 foods, and a community of more than 6 million members. With traffic of around 3.2 million every month, it is one of the best sites for those who believe in watching what they eat. The largest source of traffic is search, which is responsible for 74.80% of visits. Direct traffic is currently at 13.93%, with referrals at 9.73%. Reposts are available&nbsp; sites such as Simplesciencefitness.com and Kalynskitchen.com. With the help of top rated mobile applications, users can monitor their diets and exercise by using a number of special features.</p>'),
(144, 'Hometalk', 'http://www.hometalk.com', 'hometalk.jpg', 1998, 190, 1, 1, 1, 4200000, 5, 4852, 0, '2015-07-15 13:08:55', 'com', 60.91, '2015-07-15 13:06:34', '<p>The best of DIY ideas for homes and gardens are available at hometalk.com. Created in 1998, the websites currently draws 4.2 million visitors a month, 84% of whom are from the United States. The biggest source of traffic is the social media, accounting for 57.63%. However, direct traffic is also significant at 30.34%. Reposts and referrals are readily available from sites such as Country Living and Buzzfeed. Hometalk is noted for its coverage of the newest ideas and trends in all things H&amp;G, including painting, pallets, crafts and kitchens. It is an excellent tool for those interested in home improvement and maintainance.</p>'),
(145, 'BoredPanda', 'http://www.boredpanda.com', 'Boredpanda.jpg', 2009, 190, 2, 3, 1, 16800000, 6, 1153, 1, '2015-12-24 00:07:41', 'com', 79.42, '2015-12-24 00:07:42', '<p>A showcase for creativity and an effective cure for boredom, BoredPanda continues to go from strength to strength. This 9 year old website, with its catchy slogan of &lsquo;pandas against boredom&rsquo;, currently enjoys over 38 million visitors every month, and its star continues to rise. Reposts from social media sites are common, with social sources accounting for 56.98% of traffic. Direct visits, meanwhile, contribute to 28.18%. Top referring sites include Imgur, Feedly and Onedio. Of social traffic, 91.79% are from Facebook. BoredPanda promises entertainment and diversion for all, in the most enjoyable way possible.</p>'),
(146, 'Archilovers', 'http://www.archilovers.com/', 'archilovers.jpg', 2009, 150, 1, 1, 1, 360000, 5, 30099, 0, '2015-11-07 00:37:59', 'com', 62.6, '2015-11-07 00:38:00', '<p>Archilovers.com - is a website that was created in the year 2009 with the purpose of connecting various people from all over the world through the medium of different projects and products. The website has a dedicated app that lets visitors access the website on the go. Joining the Archilovers community is extremely simple and fast, and once the user has become a member they can easily share their professional profile along with all the projects they are involved in. With 360k visitors every month, Archilovers has a global rank of 46,961 and is extremely popular in Italy. The content is reposted by Edilportale and Archiproducts.</p>'),
(147, 'Snapguide', 'https://snapguide.com/', 'snapguide.jpg', 2009, 90, 2, 3, 1, 870000, 5, 26256, 0, '2015-10-18 21:01:31', 'com', 57.91, '2015-10-18 21:01:32', '<p>Snapguide provides how-to guides and resources for all kinds of artwork, showcasing and aiding creativity and craftsmanship on a global level. Be it gardening, arts and crafts, food and deserts and lots more, it attracts 860000 visitors on a monthly basis, of whom 82.92% are due to searches. Direct and referrals account jointly for 11% of traffic. References and reposts are common from Lifehacker and Buzzfeed, and Pinterest is responsible for 66.91% of social media traffic. Snapguide has built a loyal following of DIY enthusiasts with its easy-to-use app and encouragement to first-time guide makers.</p>'),
(148, 'Internet Bilboards ', 'http://www.internetbillboards.net/', 'internetbillboards.jpg', 2010, 90, 1, 1, 1, 40000, 2, 46456, 0, '2015-10-18 21:06:22', 'net', 37.89, '2015-10-18 21:06:23', '<p><strong></strong>Internet Billboards, which considers itself to be a digital hubspot, features both original content as well as carefully curated digital content. It&rsquo;s fresh and innovative approach is thought provoking and interesting. This site gets around 30000 visitors every month, the majority of whom are from India or the United States. 71.24% of its traffic is direct, with another 15.98% from search. Referrals and reposts are to be found on sites such as Entrepreneur.com and Spiritsoftware.biz. Of social traffic, Facebook and Stumbleupon are the biggest contributors. With its engaging design and engrossing content, Internet Billboards is one to watch.</p>'),
(149, 'iPhoneCaptaiN', 'http://www.iphonecaptain.com/', 'iphonecaptain.jpg', 2011, 150, 1, 1, 0, 45000, 3, 407551, 1, '2016-01-08 21:34:00', 'com', 28.42, '2016-01-08 21:34:02', '<p>iPhoneCaptaiN &ndash; For users looking to keep up on the latest news in the world of iOS, iPhoneCaptaiN is a great find, with tools such as how-to tutorials, reviews, and tweaks. Of it''s more than 30000 visitors every month, a whopping 79.92% of traffic is from search, with 17.49% from direct. Referrals and reposts are mostly from About.me and Feedly.com. Most of social traffic is generated from Reddit (57.91%) and Twitter (26.27%), with Facebook moving in third at around 8.42%. iPhoneCaptaiN is a great way to stay posted on the latest developments in iOS, which move at a famously quick pace.</p>'),
(150, 'Lera Blog', 'http://lerablog.org/', 'LeraBlog.jpg', 2007, 150, 1, 1, 1, 45000, 5, 23232, 0, '2015-07-18 18:19:40', 'org', 43.56, '2015-07-18 18:19:41', '<p>Lera Blog prides itself on being a comprehensive source of information on a variety of topics, including but not limited to advertising and marketing, media and entertainment, and business and finance. It currently generates traffic of around 50000 every month, of which 37.27% are direct visits and 52.76% are from search. The 6.45% of traffic generated by referrals are due to reposts from sites such as Lockerdome.com and yourbrandingauthority.com. The social media component is represented by Twitter (34.26%) and Stumbleupon (21.05%), with Stack Exchange making up a not insignificant 12.32% of social traffic. Lera Blog is a great resource for the well-informed reader.</p>'),
(151, 'CustomerThink', 'http://customerthink.com/', 'customerthink.jpg', 2002, 190, 1, 1, 1, 110000, 6, 64579, 0, '2015-11-07 20:40:11', 'com', 68.7, '2015-11-07 20:40:13', '<p>This online community functions at a global level, and represents the efforts of business leaders to create enterprises which are truly customer-centric. It gets around 130000 visits every month, from over 118 countries. Traffic is mostly search driven (53.01%), though direct visits also play a significant part, generating 31.41% of traffic. Referrals and reposts can be found at Feedly.com and Formstack.com. Social traffic is generated mostly through Twitter (63.19%), but Facebook is responsible for a significant 16.68%. CustomerThink has received positive attention due to its coverage of relevant issues such as Customer Experience Management, Customer Relationship Management and Social Business.</p>'),
(152, 'Tripwolf ', 'http://www.tripwolf.com/', 'tripwolf.jpg', 2006, 90, 2, 3, 1, 150000, 5, 87684, 0, '2016-02-03 21:24:52', 'com', 59.81, '2016-02-03 21:24:53', '<p>Tripwolf is a popular and trusted online travel guide, with information for more than 50,000 travel destinations. With 170,000 visitors and more every month, traffic sources are mainly search (72.35%) and direct visits (19.29%). Referrals are from travel sites such as Travel.alltop.com, and other sites such as Hukd.mydealz.de. Social traffic is mostly generated from Facebook (51.91%) and Twitter (21.02%), though Reddit does account for another 16.36%. Tripwolf features interesting blogs, a well-designed app, and lots of resources for the discerning travel, not to mention information of destinations anywhere from Europe to Oceania. It is a travel guide as well as a travel community, all in one place.</p>'),
(153, 'AuthorsDen', 'http://www.authorsden.com/', 'autorsden.jpg', 1999, 150, 1, 1, 1, 80000, 5, 159966, 0, '2016-02-02 00:07:45', 'com', 61.7, '2016-02-02 00:07:45', '<p>AuthorsDen.com is a place where readers and writers interact and engage in a dynamic, interesting forum. It features 388,825 titles and 2,444,801 reviews. Traffic is currently at 80,000 visits every month, with 63.16% of visits being search driven and another 18.91% direct. Social traffic accounts for 9.97% of all traffic, of which 57.51% is generated by Pinterest, 29.75% from Twitter and 11.77% from Facebook. Referrals are mostly commonly from such sites as Snapjudgment.org, Readersintheknow.com and Educationworld.com. Authors, with the help of this site, can reach millions of readers annually, interacting with fans and keeping them posted.</p>'),
(154, 'BiggerPockets', 'http://www.biggerpockets.com/', 'biggerpockets.jpg', 2003, 450, 1, 1, 1, 1600000, 5, 8521, 0, '2015-07-18 18:43:14', 'com', 69.43, '2015-07-18 18:43:16', '<p>BiggerPockets encourages users to take control of their financial futures with the help of careful real estate investments and good advice. It operates like a social network, so that users can, at any point, engage with other users in order to develop skills, knowledge and confidence. It generates traffic of 1.4 million visits every month, and search and direct are responsible for the lion&rsquo;s share of these (40.67% and 40.52% respectively). Entrepreneur.com, Protopage.com, Addthis.com and Feedly.com are the biggest sources of referrals and reposts. As far as social traffic is concerned, Facebook is the most significant, generating 62.73%.</p>'),
(155, 'CraftStylish', 'http://www.craftstylish.com/', 'craftstylish.jpg', 2007, 150, 1, 1, 1, 90000, 5, 128731, 0, '2015-07-18 18:50:08', 'com', 56.28, '2015-07-18 18:50:09', '<p>CraftStylish is the kind of site that teaches enthusiasts to rework recycling materials to make beautiful vases, or create Dorset buttons out of yarn. At present, CraftStylish receives more than 100,000 visitors every month, with 13.82% of traffic direct, 22.70% from referrals, 36.20% from search and 27.03% from social. Reposts can be found at Sewingsupport.com and Premeditatedleftovers.com. Of social traffic, Pinterest is the main contributor, generating 92.33%.</p>'),
(156, 'Built in Chicago ', 'http://www.builtinchicago.org/', 'builtinchicago.jpg', 2010, 190, 1, 1, 0, 270000, 6, 64767, 1, '2015-11-16 22:23:37', 'org', 53.38, '2015-11-16 22:23:39', '<p>Built in Chicago is a hub for startups and new tech in the city. Users can stay posted on the most recent developments in the startup world, and find out exactly what&rsquo;s happening. Built in Chicago&rsquo;s gets over 270000 visits every month. Traffic is mostly direct, at 45.62%, but search accounts for around 32.66% and referrals for 12.76%. Referrals and reposts are mostly from Builtin.com, Tinyurl.com and Feedly.com. Social traffic is mostly Facebook driven (48.51%), but the contribution of Twitter has also become significant (30.48%). Built in Chicago is a great resource for startup developers and would be employees based in Chicago.</p>'),
(157, 'RealTown Blog', 'http://blogs.realtown.com/', 'realtown.jpg', 1998, 90, 1, 1, 1, 50000, 4, 99242, 0, '2015-10-18 21:09:53', 'com', 0, '2015-10-18 21:09:54', '<p>RealTown Blog<strong> -</strong> is a blog forum that specializes in real estate blogs and listings. It serves as the perfect tool for realtors who are interested in establishing a strong online presence and allows users to create blogs. The RealTown network provides users the opportunity to harness the power of communities and groups, and send messages to other users in the vicinity. With an estimated 15k visits and the content of the site being extremely popular in the United States, the blogs from the site are featured on Wamda and Dwellaware. The site has been active since 1998 and continues to provide high quality real estate content to its members.</p>'),
(158, 'SportsBlog', 'http://www.sportsblog.com/', 'sportsblog.jpg', 2002, 190, 1, 1, 0, 890000, 5, 32136, 1, '2016-03-02 20:51:38', 'com', 51.27, '2016-03-02 20:51:40', '<p>Sportsblog.com - is a blog website dedicated to providing visitors with a constant stream of new, authentic and comprehensive sports commentary and news. The site posts submissions from some of the most famous names in the field of online sports journalism and even puts up content written by thousands of influential fans from across the world as well as athlete bloggers. The site was established in the year 2002 and still continues to remain one of the most authoritative online destinations for sports news and content. A haven for sports lovers, it receives traffic of 3.40 million and holds a worldwide rank of 10,982. Content from this site is reposted by Dribble, Philboxing and Pinoygreats.</p>'),
(159, 'GameSkinny', 'http://www.gameskinny.com/', 'gameskinny.jpg', 2012, 250, 1, 1, 1, 1400000, 4, 26882, 1, '2016-02-04 10:53:03', 'com', 48.75, '2015-09-07 19:39:25', '<p>GameSkinny - is a haven for gamers since it brings all the latest news and reviews related to the latest and upcoming Xbox One, PS4, Wii-U, Xbox 360, PC, PS3, Wii, PSP, iPhone and Android games. There is lots of content to choose from on the site for avid gamers and the best part is that most of the content is contributed by avid gamers who understand the needs of modern video game players. Created in 2012, the site boasts of a worldwide rank of 32,262 with most of the traffic coming in from the United States. With a 1.40 million strong visitor base, the content of the site is reposted by sites like N4g and Guild Wars Temple.</p>'),
(160, 'Cdnis.edu.hk', 'http://www.cdnis.edu.hk/', 'cdnis.jpg', 1998, 90, 1, 1, 0, 70000, 5, 282578, 0, '2015-11-30 21:21:03', 'edu', 39.37, '2015-11-30 21:21:04', '<p>Cdnis.edu.hk - based out of Hong Kong was created in the year 1998 and is the official website of the Canadian International School of Hong Kong. It provides visitors with a detailed overview of the various features of the school along with a comprehensive list of upcoming events and news. The online newsletter of the school can be directly accessed from the website and you are able to check out all the major highlights of the institution. The maximum number of visitors of the website are from Hong Kong followed by the United States and the website receives close to 70k visitors, which explains the global ranking of 245,227.</p>'),
(161, 'BetterNetworker.com', 'http://www.betternetworker.com/', 'betternetworker.jpg', 2007, 90, 1, 1, 1, 40000, 4, 76027, 0, '2015-10-18 21:12:25', 'com', 51.58, '2015-10-18 21:12:27', '<p>Betternetworker.com- is the leading social community throughout the globe for home business, mini and direct sales representatives with an active visitor base of 30k. One of the main reasons that contribute to the popularity of the website is the fact that it offers free training to the users who wish to understand the best methods and practices for marketing their business online. The site enjoys a worldwide ranking of 570,572 and enjoys the majority of its traffic from the United States. Created in 2007, the website posts high quality content that is often reposted by sites like Jaysonlinereviews and Backlinkwatch.</p>'),
(162, 'GrindTV', 'http://www.grindtv.com/', 'grindtv.jpg', 2005, 48, 1, 1, 0, 2300000, 7, 8718, 1, '2015-11-01 20:44:01', 'com', 77.23, '2015-11-01 20:44:02', ''),
(163, 'MyTechLogy', 'http://www.mytechlogy.com/', 'mytechlogy.jpg', 2011, 90, 2, 1, 1, 50000, 4, 62891, 1, '2016-03-24 15:57:54', 'com', 37.59, '2015-11-01 14:18:51', '<p>Mytechlogy.com - is a collaborative platform that aims to bring technology enthusiasts and professionals from across the world into a single space for the purpose of sharing technology blogs, learning various IT courses, and finding IT jobs and careers in the field of technology. The site enjoys visitor strength of 40k and the majority of them are from India. The website was founded in 2011 and operates out of Singapore. The content of the site deals with technology news and information and is extremely helpful. This is why it is often reposted by various websites, including Contactsingapore and Feedly.</p>'),
(164, 'Savor the Success', 'http://www.savorthesuccess.com/', 'savor.jpg', 2008, 190, 1, 1, 0, 35000, 0, 160410, 1, '2016-03-02 21:26:51', 'com', 42.12, '2016-03-02 21:26:56', '<p>Savorthesuccess.com - is a premium business website that caters exclusively to women entrepreneurs. It is a platform where female entrepreneurs and businesswomen are able to freely connect with one another, share insights and suggestions, offer valuable advice, acquire a boost in public relations, and expand their presence on the Internet. Launched in 2008 from California, U.S., it comes as no surprise that a niche website like this would have a dedicated following with close to 45k visitors. The site has a worldwide ranking of 330,336 and it receives the majority of its traffic from the United States. The content of the site is often reposted by Entrepreneur and Skilled Up.</p>'),
(165, 'HubPages', 'http://hubpages.com/', 'hubpages.jpg', 2005, 150, 2, 1, 1, 12300000, 6, 1177, 0, '2015-12-24 00:22:53', 'com', 89.09, '2015-12-24 00:22:55', '<p>Hubpages.com - is a popular online platform for users to share and exchange their reviews, views, advice, tips, insights and opinions with different authors from around the world. One of the main selling points of Hubpages is that it is entirely free of charge and users are able to access the website without any issues. Moreover, it helps the members of the site to earn online ad revenue. Created in 2005, the site receives more than 30 million visitors each month which speaks volumes about the quality of the content available and ranks 2799 globally. The content of the site is often reposted by IGN and Sacredscribes.</p>'),
(166, 'Techtiplib', 'https://www.techtiplib.com/', 'Techtiplib.jpg', 2012, 90, 1, 1, 1, 60000, 0, 252291, 1, '2016-02-05 17:51:12', 'com', 37.62, '2015-11-01 14:51:07', '<p>Techtiplib.com - is a blog that caters to users interested in technology. There are loads of tech tips available at the site along with freeware and downloadable games. The site hosts numerous software giveaways and offers technology reviews. You can even download free ebooks from the website and all these factors combined together contribute to its popularity. With a global rank of 492,510, the website receives close to 60k visitors and most of them are from the United States. Though the website was created in 2012, it has garnered a loyal fanbase thanks to the quality content which is often reposted by websites like Anonymz and Malwaretips.</p>'),
(167, 'BLOGS.naturalnews.com', 'http://blogs.naturalnews.com/', 'Blogsnaturalnews.jpg', 2005, 250, 1, 1, 1, 270000, 3, 4612, 0, '2015-11-01 14:58:13', 'com', 88.49, '2015-11-01 14:58:14', '<p>Blogs.naturalnews.com - is a blog that provides users with expert health tips on how to live naturally. The content on the site is very helpful for visitors interested in the field of natural living and the website keeps track of all the newest natural products in the market, offers good advice and suggestions and basically provides a forum where the users are able to share their views and pose their questions regarding natural products and lifestyle. The site receives close to 300k visitors and more than half of it is from the United States. The site was first launched in the year 2005.</p>'),
(168, 'Digital Information World ', 'http://www.digitalinformationworld.com/', 'Digitalinformationworld.jpg', 2013, 250, 2, 1, 1, 120000, 3, 66078, 0, '2015-11-01 15:08:20', 'com', 53.17, '2015-11-01 15:08:21', '<p>Digitalinformationworld.com - is a splendidly organized and detailed visual stream that provides users with access with numerous digital data on varying topics, ranging from social media and marketing to business and education, technology, among others. The news and articles posted on the site are all up-to-date and the site was set up in the year 2013. The website enjoys a worldwide ranking of 196,537 and gets most of its traffic from the United States. This online telecommunications channel enjoys a lot of popularity due to its rich content and receives close to 150k visitors. Content taken from the site is regularly reposted by other websites like Feedly and Socialmediatoday.</p>'),
(169, 'Andy Sowards Blog', 'http://www.andysowards.com/blog/', 'andysowards.jpg', 2008, 190, 1, 1, 1, 85000, 4, 161411, 1, '2015-11-06 13:16:14', 'com', 40.81, '2015-11-01 15:18:32', '<p>Andy Sowards Blog - offers high quality ideas, experiments and inspirations on web design, development, social media, programming, SEO, logo design, consulting, among others. Users can go through all the information for their own benefit and read the insightful contributions from guest authors covering various topics in the industry. The main aim of this website is to provide resources and inspirations to creative users in the field. The site receives close to 100k visitors and has a global Internet ranking of 302,965.&nbsp; It is extremely popular and was first launched in 2008. The content that is posted by the website is often reposted on Design-news, Feedly and Designyoutrust.</p>'),
(170, 'InfiniGEEK', 'http://infinigeek.com/', 'infinigeek.jpg', 2012, 150, 1, 1, 1, 65000, 2, 353997, 3, '2015-12-23 13:11:57', 'com', 36.29, '2015-11-01 15:26:19', '<p>Infinigeek.com - is the perfect lifestyle website for fans of geek culture. There is an entire community waiting to be explored by the users and you can look forward to plenty of interesting geek-centric technology and science news and content, including images, forums, videos, among others. Created in 2012, the website operates out of Texas and remains one of the authoritative websites on contemporary geek culture on the Internet. Accessible through different devices, the site receives 75k visitors and the majority of them are from the United States. The website enjoys a global ranking of 374,136 and the content of the site is reposted by others like N4g and Pixshark.</p>'),
(171, 'WarriorForum Blogs', 'http://www.warriorforum.com/blogs/', 'Warriorforum.jpg', 2001, 150, 1, 1, 1, 5000000, 3, 1340, 0, '2015-11-01 15:43:46', 'com', 78.98, '2015-11-01 15:43:48', '<p>WarriorForum - is one of the best marketing forums and marketplaces on the Internet and offers tons of marketing tips and news to the users. It basically provides a platform for marketers from different industries to get together and swap suggestions, tips, opinions, views, and even increase their presence on the Internet. The website is available on various platforms including Android which explains why it is so popular, attracting close to 5 million visitors. The site enjoys a global ranking of 5,644 and in the United States, it ranks 2,472. Launched in 2001, the site continues to post fresh and relevant industry content and is often reposted by BestBlackHatForum and Alexa.</p>'),
(172, 'Slashdot', 'http://slashdot.org/', 'slashdot.jpg', 1997, 180, 1, 1, 0, 9000000, 7, 1696, 1, '2015-11-10 23:16:51', 'org', 95.72, '2015-11-10 23:16:52', '<p>Slashdot.org - is an online news source that gets updated at regular intervals to bring visitors the latest news, focusing mainly on topics connected to Open Source issues as well as Linux. The niche nature of the website means that it has a dedicated following of users who are interested in the articles and the content. The site focuses on quality and relevance and has been doing the same since its launch in the 1997. The site receives close to 9 million visitors and enjoys a worldwide website ranking of 3,660. The content posted on the site often gets reposted by popular sites like Feedly, Ustart and Ighome.</p>'),
(173, 'Edublogs', 'http://edublogs.org/', 'edublogs.jpg', 2005, 190, 1, 1, 1, 2200000, 7, 7234, 0, '2015-11-01 16:35:22', 'org', 86.34, '2015-11-01 16:35:23', '<p>Edublogs.org - is reputed for being the foremost education blogging service and caters to students and teachers around the world. It has received accolades from some of the leading international institutions and holds the interest of the users by facilitating amazing discussions and serving as a substitute for the paper newsletter. It allows for the posting and sharing of podcasts, videos and documents and enables you to create comprehensive class publications. The website was created back in 2005 and receives close to 2.2 million visitors. The website holds a global ranking of 19,572 and the content posted by the website is often reposted by Feedly, Symbaloo, Theedublogger.</p>'),
(174, 'iMedia Connection', 'http://www.imediaconnection.com/', 'imediaconnection.jpg', 2001, 590, 1, 1, 2, 270000, 6, 35088, 0, '2015-11-06 23:44:01', 'com', 74.18, '2015-11-06 23:44:02', '<p>Imediaconnection.com - is a website that provides users with access to the latest news and features relevant to the online marketing industry. Created in 2001, the website operates out of Texas and boasts of a visitor strength of 300k. The website can be accessed through a dedicated application and provides only quality content to the users. The global website ranking of Imediaconnection is 100,454 and it enjoys the most popularity in the United States where it holds a rank of 39, 819. The content available on the site always maintains its relevance to the online marketing sector and is reposted by other websites like Forbes, Cmo and Feedly.</p>'),
(175, 'Seeking Alpha', 'http://seekingalpha.com/', 'seeking alpha.jpg', 2004, 390, 1, 1, 1, 8700000, 6, 1402, 0, '2015-11-01 17:03:16', 'com', 88.02, '2015-11-01 17:03:17', '<p>Seekingalpha.com - is a website that specializes in connecting users to the best stock market insights along with accurate financial analysis. The site offers plenty of services to visitors including free earnings call transcripts, ETF, investment ideas. However, one of the most popular aspects of the website is the well-researched and crisply written articles and content penned by the finance experts who understand the nuances of the industry. It is mainly because of this content that close to 10.80 million users flock to the website. The website which was founded in 2004 has a worldwide ranking of 1937 and the content often gets reposted by Marketwatch and Nasdaq.</p>'),
(176, 'TravelPod', 'http://www.travelpod.com/', 'travelpod.jpg', 1998, 150, 1, 1, 0, 380000, 6, 36177, 1, '2016-03-03 17:06:48', 'com', 74.76, '2016-03-03 17:06:50', '<p>Travelpod.com - is a unique travel blog website that allows the users to create travel blogs for free within a short amount of time so that they find a platform where they are able to share stories and experiences about a particular trip on the go or save the precious memories in book format. The site, which was established back in 1998, is available in the form of a mobile application also for the convenience of the users and manages to attract almost 550k visitors. With a global rank of 47,433, the website receives the majority of its traffic from the United States and the content is often reposted by Tripadvisor.</p>'),
(177, 'MagPress', 'http://www.magpress.com/', 'magpress.jpg', 2004, 290, 1, 1, 0, 45000, 5, 55602, 0, '2015-11-06 23:45:07', 'com', 78.27, '2015-11-05 22:38:07', '<p>Magpress.com - is a website that hosts an impressive collection of more than 350 magazine WordPress themes as well as Responsive WordPress themes. The best part is that all of them are available for free to the users and support the WordPress Multisite owing to their user-friendly Theme Options panel. Established in the year 2004, Magpress receives close to 50k visitors and this has contributed to its worldwide website ranking of 454,788 with most of its traffic flowing in from the United States and India. The high quality WordPress themes offered by the site are often reposted by others like Colorlib, Designscrazed and Codexcoder.</p>'),
(178, 'Dezzain', 'http://www.dezzain.com/', 'dezzain.jpg', 2007, 350, 1, 1, 0, 90000, 2, 55811, 0, '2015-11-06 23:47:11', 'com', 76.15, '2015-11-05 22:45:51', '<p>Dezzain.com - specializes in providing the users with various helpful tips and online tutorials for the purpose of website development. It also provides access to innumerable SEO tips, reviews of marketing and hosting tools, software and designer and developer resources. The main USP of this website is that it enables the user to enjoy all these valuable resources and hints for free. Created in 2007, the website attracts most of its traffic from the United States and Japan, and receives close to 100k visitors. This has led to a worldwide website ranking of 319,914 and the content found on the website is often reposted by Designscrazed and WordPress.</p>'),
(179, 'WellSphere', 'http://www.wellsphere.com', 'wellsphere.jpg', 2006, 150, 1, 1, 2, 85000, 3, 162072, 0, '2015-11-06 23:49:28', 'com', 66.98, '2015-11-05 22:58:01', '<p>Wellsphere.com - was created in 2006 and mainly serves as an online community where people from all over the world can connect with health enthusiasts and professionals in order to educate and inspire one another about fitness, health and well-being. It is available for free and allows the users to benefit from the rich content that promotes better lifestyle. With more than 80k visitors, the website receives the majority share of its traffic from the United States where it has a rank of 79,591. On the other hand, the global ranking of the website is currently 215,368 and the content is frequently reposted by other websites like Greatist.</p>'),
(180, 'IndyaRocks', 'http://indyarocks.com/', 'indyarocks.jpg', 2006, 90, 1, 1, 1, 320000, 3, 24065, 0, '2015-11-05 23:05:20', 'com', 66.27, '2015-11-05 23:05:21', '<p>Indyarocks.com - is a unique website that provides users with access to various profiles. They are able to play free games and listen to their favorite tunes all the while checking out different photographs and sending SMS messages for free. The site mainly caters to the singular tastes of the Indian audience but receives most of its traffic from the United States and India. In the U.S., the website holds a rank of 52,046 while its worldwide website ranking is currently 81,489. Created in 2006, Indyarocks receives close to 320k visitors and serves up high quality content that is reposted by Blackhatworld and Edwinvaldezwordpress.</p>'),
(181, 'News24', 'http://www.news24.com/', 'news24.jpg', 1997, 290, 1, 1, 1, 8300000, 7, 1808, 0, '2015-11-05 23:11:46', 'com', 82.71, '2015-11-05 23:11:47', '<p>News24.com - receives close to 9 million visitors every month and with good reason. The website serves as the leading source of news in South Africa and always provides the users with access to the latest breaking news. The site covers news stories from Africa and the rest of the world along with great sports content, technology updates and reviews, and entertainment gossip. Established in 1997, the site can be accessed through dedicated applications and has a worldwide ranking of 4,786. Most of the website traffic is generated in South Africa and the high quality content is often picked up and reposted by Fin24, Channel24 and MWEB.</p>'),
(182, 'Wikinut', 'http://www.wikinut.com/', 'wikinut.jpg', 2009, 90, 1, 1, 1, 140000, 3, 70243, 0, '2015-11-05 23:17:35', 'com', 44.68, '2015-11-05 23:17:36', '<p>Wikinut.com - is a special website that provides users with the opportunity to write about whatever interest they have or topic that attracts them. The best part is that it is the website that pays advertising royalties to the users for their contribution. The editor is easy to use and the website accepts feedback from the readers. Payments are made quickly via PayPal. The website was created in 2009 and operates out of England but receives the maximum visitors from the United States and India. Wikinut has a global website ranking of 233,837 and gets almost 100k visitors a month. The content found on the website is often reposted by Alexaboostup, Buzzfeed, and Ranksignals.</p>'),
(183, 'Tech.pro', 'http://tech.pro/blogs', 'techpro.jpg', 2005, 190, 1, 1, 2, 860000, 4, 307331, 0, '2015-12-24 00:17:36', 'pro', 39.51, '2015-12-24 00:17:27', '<p>Tech.pro Blogs - is the blog section of a website that plays host to a professional network which was created exclusively as a platform for tech enthusiasts and developers to interact freely with one another. Not only does the site provide helpful content and tips, it allows colleagues to reconnect with one another, share their expertise in the field, and get valuable advice from the industry veterans. The blogs garner 860k visitors each month and lends to the worldwide website ranking of 47,686. Most of the traffic comes from the United States and the content is often reposted by other websites like Codeproject, Echojs, and Techbrij.</p>'),
(184, 'Seekyt ', 'http://seekyt.com/', 'seekyt.jpg', 2010, 90, 1, 1, 1, 45000, 4, 75706, 0, '2015-11-07 00:11:15', 'com', 37.78, '2015-11-07 00:11:16', '<p>Seekyt.com - is a website that pays the users to write and contribute good quality articles and content in the form of tutorials, recipes, local reviews and more. It serves as a platform where budding writers can not only hone their skills but also get paid for their valuable contributions. The website makes it a point to publish as much knowledge content as it can and the aim of the site is to make the world a wiser place. Seekyt was created in the year 2010 and out of its monthly visitor base of 50k, most of them are from the U.S., the U.K., and India with a global worldwide ranking of 484,602. The website content is reposted by Slickdeals and Creativescratch.</p>'),
(185, 'My Customer', 'http://www.mycustomer.com/', 'mycustomer.jpg', 2001, 150, 1, 1, 0, 85000, 5, 63672, 1, '2016-03-02 20:52:04', 'com', 53.55, '2016-03-02 20:52:08', '<p>Mycustomer.com - is a website that offers news content and resources to the visitors for the purpose of CRM, customer relationship management, sales, customer services, IT and marketing. It mainly targets the IT crowd and manages to rake in almost 120k users every month from around the world. However, the majority of its traffic comes from the United Kingdom followed by the United States. The website was created in 2001 and operates out of England. The worldwide website ranking of Mycustomer is 235,034 and the content that is available on the website is often reposted by other popular sites like Feedly, Cmo, Paper and Designthinkersacademy.</p>'),
(186, 'CaringBridge', 'http://www.caringbridge.org/', 'caringbridge.jpg', 2001, 180, 2, 1, 1, 1600000, 7, 8246, 0, '2015-11-07 00:36:02', 'org', 86.93, '2015-11-07 00:36:03', '<p>Caringbridge.org - is a nonprofit website that is entirely committed towards bringing friends and family from across the world together at the beginning of any kind of health journey. It provides a personal space where users are able to share their innermost thoughts and feelings with their loved ones and it is easy to get started on the website. The website, created in 2001, operates out of Minnesota, U.S., and can be accessed from different devices with the help of a dedicated application. The site has close to 2 million visitors and enjoys a global website ranking of 16,134. The majority of the traffic emerges from the United States.</p>'),
(187, 'Mahara.ccv.edu', 'https://mahara.ccv.edu/', 'ccvedu.jpg', 2002, 48, 1, 1, 1, 55000, 0, 266469, 2, '2015-11-26 14:07:58', 'edu', 52.97, '2015-11-07 20:29:28', '<p>Ccv.edu - Community College of Vermont is a website that seeks to lend the necessary support and at the same time challenge every student in meeting their goals in the field of education via a wholesome commitment to access, success and affordability. Created in the year 2002, the website operates out of Vermont, U.S. and strives to fulfil the study goals of the visitors. The website receives close to 60k visitors every month and enjoys a worldwide website ranking of 200,462. Most of the traffic generated from the website comes from the U.S. and the content that is posted on the site is often reposted by websites like Jobsinvt and Vsc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Post will be published in the section: https://mahara.ccv.edu</p>'),
(188, 'Mahara.uncc.edu', 'https://mahara.uncc.edu/', 'unccedu.jpg', 1988, 48, 1, 1, 0, 2000, 0, 16089, 1, '2015-11-30 21:00:30', 'edu', 73.95, '2015-11-30 21:00:32', '<p>Uncc.edu - is the official website of the fourth largest campus of the UNC, which wholeheartedly devotes itself to expert public service, teaching and practical research. The latest information and news about the institution can be found on the site and it is accessed by almost 1.40 million visitors on a monthly basis. The website can be accessed through dedicated apps and is also available on social media. The website enjoys a worldwide website ranking of 17,801 and the majority of the visitors are from the United States. The content that is posted by the website often gets reposted by other sites like Worldcat and Myinterfase.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Important:<br /><br />Post will be published in the section: https://mahara.uncc.edu/</p>'),
(189, 'Homeenergypros.lbl.gov', 'http://homeenergypros.lbl.gov/', 'homeenergypros.jpg', 2006, 150, 2, 1, 1, 50000, 5, 29269, 0, '2015-11-07 21:03:11', 'gov', 87.77, '2015-11-07 21:03:12', '<p>Homeenergypros.lbl.gov - is a GOV social network that is created specifically for professionals associated with the field of home energy. This unique digital community caters to the needs and requirements of the users who work in the arena of home energy performance, and the site is updated frequently with new articles and news stories about the latest development in the industry. The high quality content posted by the website is highly valued by the visitors and since its creation in 2006, the site, which operates out of New Jersey, has received almost 50k visitors every month. The website receives the majority of its traffic from the United States.</p>'),
(190, 'CareerAddict', 'http://www.careeraddict.com/', 'careeraddict.jpg', 2013, 250, 1, 1, 0, 300000, 3, 68123, 0, '2015-11-10 02:57:52', 'com', 32.89, '2015-11-07 21:09:45', '<p>Careeraddict.com - was created in the year 2013 and provides visitors with all the updated information they require in order to excel in their daily lives. The main purpose of the website is to provide advice and daily inspiration, and this allows the users to develop, learn, contribute and become the best there is. The content found on the site helps them reach their full potential. The site receives close to 300000 visitors every month and this has helped it reach the global ranking of 40,791. The maximum number of website users is from the Philippines and the United States.</p>'),
(191, 'TechCrunch', 'http://techcrunch.com/', 'techcrunch.jpg', 2005, 1600, 1, 1, 2, 30800000, 8, 482, 1, '2015-11-20 00:15:36', 'com', 93.52, '2015-11-20 00:15:37', '<p>TechCrunch is a trendy technology site that specializes in information relevant and useful for technology start-ups. The site has been running since 2005, has over 120 associated domains, and has become a go-to for all users who want the latest news related to start-up technology. The majority of the site&rsquo;s traffic, over 50%, comes from users in the United States. TechCrunch&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on websites like Feedly.com and Techmeme.com. The site gets the majority (34%) of its traffic from direct site visits, with search based traffic coming at a close 30%. Out of these, nearly 90% are organic searches.</p>'),
(192, 'Engadget', 'http://www.engadget.com/', 'engadget.jpg', 2004, 490, 1, 1, 1, 79700000, 8, 392, 0, '2016-03-02 23:05:25', 'com', 94.14, '2016-03-02 23:05:25', '<p>Engadget is a popular e-magazine website that offers comprehensive insights into the latest gadgets and other consumer electronics. The site offers insights into how technology impacts our daily lives. It was created in 2004 and gets over 80 million visitors every month, who spend an average of four minutes on the site. The majority of the site&rsquo;s visitors are from the United States (38%), with Japanese users coming in second (10%). The site receives over half its traffic from direct site visits, with referrals accounting for a mere 10% of total traffic. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted of Feddly.com and ighome.com.</p>'),
(193, 'Entrepreneur', 'http://www.entrepreneur.com/', 'entrepreneur.jpg', 1994, 1900, 1, 1, 0, 17500000, 7, 946, 0, '2015-11-24 20:32:54', 'com', 90.35, '2015-11-24 20:32:55', '<p>Entrepreneur - is a great website for business insider news, advice and general tips. The site specializes in useful information for the budding entrepreneur and ranks in the top 30 websites of its category.&nbsp; Created over 20 years ago, in 1994, Entrepreneur receives over 18 million users a month, most of whom are from the United States. A whopping 40% of the site&rsquo;s traffic comes from search engine results, with over 99% being organic keyword searches. The website&rsquo;s content is routinely posted on sites like Feedly and Foxnews.com. The site also receives about a quarter of its traffic from social media sites like Facebook and Twitter.</p>'),
(194, 'TheStreet', 'http://www.thestreet.com/', 'thestreet.jpg', 1997, 1200, 1, 1, 0, 6700000, 6, 2157, 0, '2015-11-24 20:33:42', 'com', 84.49, '2015-11-24 20:33:43', '<p>TheStreet.com is a popular website that provides relevant financial news to investors and those that follow the stock market. Apart from news and information, the site also features award winning stock-analysis and market data. The site receives nearly 7 million users every year, making it a fairly credible site. Created in 1997, the street receives nearly 90% of all its traffic from users in the United States. More than half of the website&rsquo;s traffic comes from web-based searches, 99% of which are based on organic keywords. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted on Msn.com and Nasdaq.com.</p>'),
(195, 'Infusionsoft', 'http://www.infusionsoft.com/', 'infusionsoft.jpg', 2002, 1200, 1, 1, 0, 37200000, 5, 397, 0, '2015-11-24 20:34:21', 'com', 70.88, '2015-11-24 20:34:22', '<p>Dealing in comprehensive sales and marketing automation software, infusion is a global leader in software development for small business. Using a combination of CRM, lead capture, email marketing, and ecommerce, InfusionSoft has been providing automation services to SMEs since 2002. The site receives over 37 million visitors in a month, 70% of who are from the United States, making it a fairly trustworthy site. The site receives most of its traffic from direct visits (39%), with malls (31%) and referrals (27%) coming in close. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted on sites like YouTube and Facebook.</p>'),
(196, 'Guardian Liberty Voice ', 'http://guardianlv.com/', 'guardianlv.jpg', 2012, 790, 1, 1, 0, 400000, 5, 43318, 0, '2015-11-24 20:35:02', 'com', 58.71, '2015-11-24 20:35:03', '<p>Guardianlv.com&nbsp;is a major source of all kinds of breaking news, movies and TV reviews. The site covers all U.S. related news, right from politics to science and technology. The site receives an estimated 400,000 visitors every month, more than half of which are from the United States, and North America. The Guardian receives over 55% of its traffic from search-based results, of which a 100% are organic searches. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted on Facebook &amp; Twitter, but barely 17% of the site&rsquo;s traffic originates from social media.</p>'),
(197, 'Bplans Blog', 'http://articles.bplans.com/', 'bplans.jpg', 1996, 990, 1, 1, 0, 650000, 6, 10118, 0, '2015-11-24 20:35:43', 'com', 68.74, '2015-11-24 20:35:45', '<p>Bplans Blog is popular source of business news for young entrepreneurs or those looking to start their own business. The site features popular blogs that discuss businesses and offers tips on how to stay in the game. Bplans Blog has been running since 1996, and gets over 650,000 visitors every month, 45% of which are from the United States. Over 70% of site&rsquo;s traffic comes via search-based results, all of which are organic searches, with social media barely contributing to even 1.50% of total traffic. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted on Paloalto.com and Mplans.com, and is associated with nearly 50 other domains.</p>'),
(198, 'Benzinga', 'http://www.benzinga.com/', 'benzinga.jpg', 2009, 590, 1, 1, 0, 1100000, 5, 16800, 0, '2015-11-24 20:36:13', 'com', 73.88, '2015-11-24 20:36:14', '<p>Benzinga.com is a financial information website that offers trading ideas &amp; advice, comprehensive stock market quotes, and other business related news. All the content on the site is published by financial professionals, making it a credible source of information. The site receives over 1.10 million visitors every month, with a bounce rate of a little over 60%. 75% of the site&rsquo;s traffic is from the United States, with direct site visits (37%) being the major source, closely followed by search-based (33%) and referral (26%) traffic. Benzinga&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on sites like Zacks.com and Prweb.com.</p>'),
(199, 'Investing.com', 'http://www.investing.com/', 'investing.jpg', 1995, 1200, 1, 1, 0, 21200000, 6, 734, 0, '2015-11-24 20:36:43', 'com', 68.54, '2015-11-24 20:36:45', '<p>Investing.com is a financial information website that offers users free real time market quotes, and other relevant market data. It ranks in the top 10 sites of its category, with over 21 million users every month. The majority of investing&rsquo;s traffic is from users in Russia (17%) and Turkey (12%). Nearly 67% of the site&rsquo;s traffic is from direct visits, with referrals contributing about 17%. The site&rsquo;s content is readily posted on Facebook and Google Accounts, and has been a reliable source of business news for nearly 20 years.</p>');
