(200, 'CNN iReport ', 'http://ireport.cnn.com/', 'CNN.jpg', 1993, 290, 1, 1, 1, 550000, 8, 78, 0, '2015-11-11 01:57:20', 'com', 100, '2015-11-11 01:57:21', '<p>CNN iReport is an interactive news portal that allows registered members to share their news stories, images and videos, with CNN and the rest of the world. The site was launched in 1993 and has been a premier source of personalized world, travel and entertainment news. It receives nearly 700,000 visitors every month, half of which are from the United States and Canada. The site receives a majority of its traffic via Social media, more specifically Facebook, which accounts for 86%. Search-based results come in second (27%), with referrals barely accounting for 20%. CNN iReport&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on Facebook.com and Cnn.com.</p>'),
(201, 'MarketingProfs', 'http://www.marketingprofs.com/', 'marketingprofs.jpg', 1999, 990, 1, 1, 0, 910000, 5, 14720, 0, '2015-11-24 20:37:38', 'com', 79.44, '2015-11-24 20:37:39', '<p>Created in 1999, MarketingProfs is a marketing resource website that is a big hit among marketers because of its various marketing-centric articles, strategies, training and tips. It ranks in the top 200 in its category, with nearly a million visitors every month and a bounce rate of above 70%; 58% of all users are from the United States. MarketingProfs receives the majority of its traffic from direct site visits (44%) and search-based results (39%), all of which are organic searches. The site&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on LinkedIn and G2crowd.</p>'),
(202, 'Hongkiat Blog', 'http://www.hongkiat.com/blog/', 'hongkiat.jpg', 2006, 990, 1, 1, 0, 9200000, 6, 2140, 0, '2015-11-24 20:40:04', 'com', 75.46, '2015-11-24 20:40:05', '<p>Hongkiat.com is a design internet blog that covers various articles, tutorials, and tips of web designers and bloggers. Launched in 2006, the site ranks number 6 in its category, making it fairly credible source of information for designers. It receives a whopping 9 million plus visitors, out of which 36% are from the United States, 10% are from India, and the rest from over 205 countries. The site receives nearly all its traffic via search results (81%), with referrals and social media contributing only 3.5 and 1.5%, respectively. The website&rsquo;s content is posted on Behance.net and Ezvid.com.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important:</strong><br />Post will be published in the section: http://www.hongkiat.com/blog/</p>'),
(203, 'BeautifulLife', 'http://www.beautifullife.info/', 'beautifullife.jpg', 2006, 290, 1, 1, 1, 279500, 6, 51527, 0, '2016-03-24 14:25:48', 'info', 50.35, '2016-03-24 14:25:48', '<p>BeautifulLife - it''s online magazine about modern trends in design. This site every day posts news from the world of design: Interior Design, Web Design, Urban Design, Fashion Design, Industrial Design, Graphic Design, Automotive Design. BeautifulLife was launched in 2006 and at the moment has over 2500 indexed web pages. News published on BeautifulLife are actively shared in social media, for example in Google Plus. The main traffic - 22% - from United States, the main source of traffic - 65% - from search engines.</p>'),
