(240, 'Blog.mt5.com', 'http://blog.mt5.com/', 'mt5.jpg', 2003, 190, 1, 1, 1, 11000, 2, 9936, 0, '2016-03-03 00:05:13', 'com', 53.8, '2016-03-03 00:05:15', '<p>Blog.mt5.com is an online platform that allows professional and novice traders to share knowledge, experience and insights in the various fields of Forex, futures, and the stock market. It&rsquo;s a great site for anyone looking for finance related information. It was created in 2003 and attracts about 100k visitors every month, with the majority of the site&rsquo;s users coming from the Ukraine (42%), and Russia coming in a close second (37%). The site receives a whopping 63% of its traffic from online referrals, with direct site visits at a 27%. The blog&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on sites like mt5.com and crypto-coins.ru.</p>'),
(241, 'HealthyWomen Community', 'http://community.healthywomen.org/', 'healthywomen.jpg', 1998, 190, 1, 1, 1, 75200, 5, 67157, 0, '2016-03-03 00:11:19', 'org', 67.47, '2016-03-03 00:11:20', '<p>HealthyWomen Community - is an online forum where every day women can connect, share their knowledge &amp; experiences with each other and life experts. The site allows members to discuss a range of topics, including nutrition &amp; fitness, beauty, illness, parenting, work, and even work-life balance.&nbsp; This website receives over 80k visitors every month, with the majority of its users being from India (29%), and another 25% from the United States. The site was created in 1998 and gets nearly half if it&rsquo;s traffic from search results, and another 40% from direct visits. The site&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on sites like semrush.com and urlopener.com.</p>'),
(242, 'Sett', 'http://sett.com/', 'sett.jpg', 1998, 90, 1, 1, 1, 67800, 4, 124694, 0, '2016-03-03 00:17:30', 'com', 47.77, '2016-03-03 00:17:31', '<p>Sett is an online community blog that allows users to build up the audience to their own website. The site is a self-help site that contains a number of tutorials and videos on how to increase their audience. It was created in 1998, and attracts over 67k visitors a month, with the majority of them being from the United States (26%), and India coming in second (23%). Sett gets nearly 43% of its traffic from search results, and direct visits contributing to about 24% of total traffic. The site&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on sites like dearblogger.org and tynan.com.</p>'),
(243, 'IM faceplate', 'http://www.imfaceplate.com/', 'imfaceplate.jpg', 2010, 150, 1, 1, 1, 64800, 2, 21036, 0, '2016-03-03 00:24:18', 'com', 35.12, '2016-03-03 00:24:19', '<p>IM faceplate&nbsp;is an online branding website that allows users to build their brands and connect with online consumers. Their internet marketing &ldquo;faceplate&rdquo; is designed to integrate users in to an online community of internet marketers. Imfaceplate was created in 2010 and attracts about 65k users every month, with the majority of them coming from India (52%), and about 13% from the United States &amp; Vietnam as well. The site gets a whopping 75% of its traffic from direct site visits, with referrals contributing to about 15% of total traffic. The site&rsquo;s content is readily reposted on sites like urlopener.com and faceseo.vn.</p>'),
(244, 'Blasting News United States', 'http://www.blastingnews.com/', 'blastingnews.jpg', 2012, 650, 1, 1, 1, 33200000, 1, 287, 0, '2016-03-24 14:15:23', 'com', 44.66, '2016-03-24 14:13:33', '<p>Post will be published in the section: http://us.blastingnews.com/</p>'),
